</P>
<P>
 Joe Magrane is expected to pitch batting practice this week for the first time 
since he had arthroscopic surgery on his left elbow last month. If he has no 
setbacks, Magrane might rejoin the rotation by late April or early May. BOB 
NIGHTENGALE 
</P>
