<DOCNO> LA032294-0076 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 025095 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
March 22, 1994, Tuesday, Ventura West Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 9; Column 1; Metro Desk 
