 * Director Ron Howard's "The Paper" is certain to make future headlines after 
Universal rolled out the witty old-fashioned newspaper drama, starring Michael 
Keaton and Glenn Close, on five screens for $175,507, or roughly $35,000 per 
screen. 04,35,18,10,10 Weekend Gross/ Screens/ Weeks in Movie (Studio) Total 
