<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA032294-0152 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 025171 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
March 22, 1994, Tuesday, Home Edition 
</P>
