<P>
CARE ENTERPRISES YEARLY PROFIT DIPS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Care Enterprises Inc., a health care provider, reported a profit of $5 
million, or 38 cents a share, for 1993, compared to $5.7 million, or 49 cents a 
share, for 1992.Revenue increased 4%, to $200.4 million from $192 million in 
1992. For the fourth quarter, profit totaled $1.1 million, or 8 cents a share, 
which included a charge of $1.1 million related to its share appreciation 
rights plan. That compares to profit of $3.2 million, or 27 cents a share, for 
the like 1992 period. Revenue rose 6%, to $52.2 million from $49.2 million. 
</P>
