REGIONAL EARNINGS: SEMTECH EARNINGS HIT $70,000 IN 4TH QUARTER 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Semtech Corp., a Newbury Park maker of electronic components, said it earned 
$70,000 in its fiscal fourth quarter ended Jan. 30, compared with a $16,000 
profit a year earlier.Semtech attributed part of the gain to sales of new 
products as the company attempts to shift from military and aerospace to 
commercial markets. 
</P>
<P>
 Its revenue in the latest quarter rose 12%, from $4.77 million to $5.36 
million. 
</P>
<P>
 For its full fiscal year, Semtech's earnings fell by nearly 50%, to $300,000, 
from $589,000 a year before. Its annual revenue increased 6%, from $20.2 
million to $21.3 million. 
