<TEXT>
<P>
 Fugro West Inc., a Ventura engineering concern that's been involved in some of 
Ventura County's most publicized -- and controversial -- development projects, 
is on an expansion binge. 
</P>
<P>
 Fugro has announced four acquisitions, bringing its staff to a total of 200 in 
11 offices throughout the West. 
</P>
<P>
 Two of the acquisitions were local: K-C Geotechnical Associates of Santa 
Barbara and the West Coast division of NCS International, based in Ventura. 
