</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA032294-0242 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 025261 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
March 22, 1994, Tuesday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part C; Page 10; Column 2; Sports Desk 
</P>
