<TEXT>
<P>
 The Hague -- In an article in last week's World Report on the cleanliness of 
European capitals, the Hague was incorrectly identified as the capital of the 
Netherlands. The Hague is the seat of government; Amsterdam is the capital. 
</P>
</TEXT>
